ss=\"mw-cite-backlink\">^ <a href=\"#cite_ref-bikeshed-blog_3-0\"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-bikeshed-blog_3-1\"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite id=\"CITEREFPoul-Henning_Kamp1999\" class=\"citation web cs1\">Poul-Henning Kamp (2 October 1999). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://phk.freebsd.dk/sagas/bikeshed\">\"The Bikeshed email\"</a>. <i>phk.freebsd.dk</i>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=phk.freebsd.dk&amp;rft.atitle=The+Bikeshed+email&amp;rft.date=1999-10-02&amp;rft.au=Poul-Henning+Kamp&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fphk.freebsd.dk%2Fsagas%2Fbikeshed&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ALaw+of+triviality\" class=\"Z3988\"></span><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r951705291\"/></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite id=\"CITEREFForsyth2009\" class=\"citation book cs1\"><a href=\"https://wikipedia.com/wiki/Donelson_R._Forsyth\" title=\"Donelson R. Forsyth\">Forsyth, Donelson R</a> (2009). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://books.google.com/books?id=RsMNiobZojIC&amp;pg=PA317\"><i>Group Dynamics</i></a> (5 ed.). Cengage Learning. p.&#160;317. <a href=\"https://wikipedia.com/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"ISBN (identifier)\">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href=\"https://wikipedia.com/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-0-495-59952-4\" title=\"Special:BookSources/978-0-495-59952-4\"><bdi>978-0-495-59952-4</bdi></a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Group+Dynamics&amp;rft.pages=317&amp;rft.edition=5&amp;rft.pub=Cengage+Learning&amp;rft.date=2009&amp;rft.isbn=978-0-495-59952-4&amp;rft.aulast=Forsyth&amp;rft.aufirst=Do